| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2023-4016 — Recovery Inhibition (lockbit3)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: e5de953f-fc6b-58e7-b154-5e8a4f335b58"
